description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&#39;Caring for your Career&#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Health Care Assistant&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Crowborough&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full Time &amp; Part Time Hours Available)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are on the look-out for Health Care Assistants with bags of energy, to deliver exceptional patient care on our ward based at our Crowborough Hospital - a centre of excellence in orthopaedics. Awarded OUTSTANDING by the CQC, we are a hospital with a difference. Not your typical working environment, we sit within the beautiful Ashdown Forest, a place where you&#39;ll have the quality time to spend with patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will play a vital role in delivering the highest standard of care and service for patients, visitors and colleagues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have the room to make a real difference, without the red tape. Working as part of a multi-disciplinary team you will ensure the Horder Centre provides an excellent, high quality, seamless patient experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Must Haves&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in patient care in a hospital or care setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication Skills, both verbal and written&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A willingness to train and work towards City &amp; Guilds/NVQs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Haves&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orthopaedic/Clinic experience will set you apart from the rest&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be based at our Crowborough Hospital - a centre of excellence in orthopaedics. Awarded OUTSTANDING by the CQC, we&#39;re a hospital with a difference. Not your typical working environment, we sit within the beautiful Ashdown Forest, a place where you&#39;ll have quality time to spend with your patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a thank you for your passion in delivering exceptional patient care, we&#39;ll care for your career, with rewards and opportunities that aren&#39;t just good - they&#39;re exceptional.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A salary benchmarked inline with the NHS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A generous pension scheme - 3% employee and 6% employer - from 3 months&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;27 days holiday (plus bank holidays) to enjoy some well deserved R&amp;R&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Private medical and Westfield Health&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free parking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Life insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A free lunch (turns out there is such a thing!)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A catalogue of unique training courses, from IT skills to leadership training with a twist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to make a real difference.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information take a look at our role brief or get in touch with the Talent Team at recruitment@horder.co.uk #TeamHorder #CaringforyourCareer&lt;/p&gt;
